---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="AETHERIA | Alta Perfumería" description="AETHERIA — Alta perfumería invisible. Fragancias de edición limitada con ingredientes exóticos como Oud de Laos y Rosa Damascena. Descubra el arte de la perfumería de lujo.">
  <Navbar />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header
    class="relative h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        alt="A moody, high-contrast black and white cinematic photograph of a master perfumer in his laboratory."
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCkrLaBTHxO8FZIrgjblZZ0ipte6wb63g6tzQVhR6KwVT_CVS5oEGciQHGPXGEhy5_3cE2_n_aQD836z4-NvSeQGyriZgwyd8vRzF0-4fjMpdpZ7MENCcNPEMIa3YDXKsxfcn5PEOpUYzcDntzxOe6EzlT2ntDKYvJ-Ezdm7x1R8soAZuOaf6SOPVqVYpWj_cjZh63AeoV7xXb-RCJkI5cWu6kDsW6IVdlSUX0HD8zuxjSLZPnypwUgC6ikgBMh629paQHGNnOpwY0l"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-margin-mobile max-w-4xl">
      <h1
        class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-white mb-8 reveal"
        data-reveal
      >
        El arte de la alta perfumería invisible.
      </h1>
      <div data-reveal style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <a
          class="inline-block px-10 py-4 border border-white text-white font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest btn-gold-hover uppercase"
          href="#collection"
        >
          Descubrir la Colección
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="py-section-gap bg-background overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile text-center">
      <span
        class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-gold-accent tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 block"
        data-reveal
      >L'ESSENCE DE L'ÂME</span
      >
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-10" data-reveal>
        Fragancias que narran historias sin palabras.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant" data-reveal>
        Nuestras creaciones son el resultado de una búsqueda obsesiva por la
        pureza. Cada gota contiene ingredientes exóticos recolectados éticamente,
        desde el Oud más profundo de Laos hasta la Rosa Damascena recogida al
        amanecer. Una arquitectura olfativa diseñada para aquellos que encuentran
        la distinción en lo imperceptible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Featured Collection -->
  <section
    class="pb-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max mx-auto"
    id="collection"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-7 group" data-reveal>
        <div class="relative aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden mb-6">
          <img
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-700 group-hover:opacity-0"
            alt="Aura Noire perfume bottle on dark wood with black silk petals."
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBy_lbXMs686FBLHH9zhwklfasW5UD2mc3U4LD77CWYpE7EOKB05QmsQaUk0mzmMPCZHoM2keIlGIusZX0e5NzxuLNqa7_2Tjyxn5R9tMwxwna1Va7vPhF2txQ6YnJomINq1tBAO0-ZyVnwz8A-BReluaXXvwf5KHkcrk2oOZhm7Cnct6mIIX-s9SgmgdIUwmcPu8me35Ep6g3t_TqCCtvjVNW24GOrZiaTuMfJRChSCPSUNkKf0VvuFyYC4FR5Uh2AlLOr_4yA8e6Z"
          />
          <img
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-700 group-hover:opacity-100"
            alt="Raw perfume ingredients: rose petals, sandalwood, amber resin."
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuArKIEFNDMil66GZTHAUoXKqqJ3zopZIY1oufheHRglr14s0u2cWS6UAzANgnidMB9kU0cCG7cVJ5xboAI2aLXp44YiFSZKJ3oFVWcbuzOcWPwNJPWbuCUAwYtUgs41SF2wMDT-woyGWZCvj8mF3VrFXb34wYdAj0J1x7j5aa7uPuAQmPvu1EvHlOkRklWVuGLHX3jKsmqnFxOngNP1Tc2EeThDXBEpjfp6Pt6FvChIPBv1vEW7tZU76RmxDWpSadrTtIvd9YED65Vr"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant pb-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
              AURA NOIRE
            </h3>
            <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant mt-1">
              Amaderado Especiado
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">$280</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-section-gap md:pt-40">
        <div class="group" data-reveal style="transition-delay: 150ms;">
          <div
            class="relative aspect-[1/1] bg-surface-container mb-6 flex items-center justify-center p-12"
          >
            <img
              class="w-2/3 h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-2xl"
              alt="Santal D'Or perfume bottle on white marble."
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBq5KDRoOGopg7a9k7yrjEpqTDnjD4hFMBmqj8oNonNl4myV2mALOv3HVq5wYIJkIgslAJBN2wzvUUrutSG4crBd_agi2zUIuJdMyozlNRqf-i6SxaFG59d4wpAX790Ls670gldN6jjtwG64GRaUJf4qi93SNYDjA_wfYURz6bfQaPunhQ9lSF8WFwo43efpzNaInioE91ITN7KoN5EElp2cojAtU4RU0amKveEaSdIhhqoXaULxzxCLHDGMfKEl2sIzkNcOBp0f-7M"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant pb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
                SANTAL D'OR
              </h3>
              <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant mt-1">
                Amaderado
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">$260</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group" data-reveal style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
          <div
            class="relative aspect-[1/1] bg-surface-container-low mb-6 flex items-center justify-center p-12"
          >
            <img
              class="w-2/3 h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-lg"
              alt="Rose Éthérée perfume bottle with soft pink tint."
              src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDG5ru2p-V5Mq09D7eeGjrO5v4aR1SCkoSK1hWBw2sk9I77-wvMC74KTgTFHPO-k8Mq78jSpkDWsPnNyCFb4ZLgtScjv51PfTGkkgvCu9hd5UFPWGWnXcG5lXcNZAcA6DgBMirqxjfNVbFKPrFjFA3MyBcOwZeQu5vi4D0d4jEuQUUVeIPhxVdoIMnAIDRCVGFytdroOocxuUXNCjKnAP2xx3sTVFU46yZvZlQZqprSa3Qxd_tAg1mAnRzEmy_28-Ew-y9n3PR1nmTb"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant pb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
                ROSE ÉTHÉRÉE
              </h3>
              <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant mt-1">
                Floral Oriental
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">$290</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Sensory Experience -->
  <section class="bg-surface-container py-section-gap overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop"
    >
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1" data-reveal>
          <img
            class="w-full aspect-square object-cover shadow-2xl"
            alt="Oriental fragrance ingredients: spices, vanilla pods, resins."
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAruypJeevE8qcVJt7iZYfys2tkVNCJyiHYh85TLleYYZqruxN-VPd4Yu9-04VxWbLTAh1H_95PFTDsWwnxY_qn0qo7rz7P8bGiNAR7Ov5OE0ePqRHRniEDo8ztIyfd8PcsCcR-J7yqawT9bln_dL-FXfdC6VNcpAKwB7nZO78d0W28P4xwXJ8Fbbj4JCjf_Ovwjeuw5_qrE4hnH-dLfKIEz2sZ-nN6k3y_WEF2CUNoJCVd2WFwS1Bbc0bRF8XEH60GIoZOPFfaNKMY"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 lg:pl-16">
          <span
            class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-gold-accent tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 block"
            data-reveal
          >EXPERIENCIA SENSORIAL</span
          >
          <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-8" data-reveal>
            Defina su identidad olfativa.
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-12" data-reveal>
            Explore nuestras familias principales y descubra la esencia que
            resuena con su narrativa personal.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4" data-reveal>
            <button
              class="p-6 border border-outline hover:border-gold-accent transition-all text-left group"
            >
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl group-hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors"
              >eco</span>
              <h4 class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest">
                CITRUS
              </h4>
            </button>
            <button
              class="p-6 border border-outline hover:border-gold-accent transition-all text-left group"
            >
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl group-hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors"
              >local_florist</span>
              <h4 class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest">
                FLORAL
              </h4>
            </button>
            <button
              class="p-6 border border-outline hover:border-gold-accent transition-all text-left group"
            >
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl group-hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors"
              >auto_awesome</span>
              <h4 class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest">
                ORIENTAL
              </h4>
            </button>
            <button
              class="p-6 border border-outline hover:border-gold-accent transition-all text-left group"
            >
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined mb-4 text-3xl group-hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors"
              >forest</span>
              <h4 class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest">
                WOODY
              </h4>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Reviews Section -->
  <section
    class="py-section-gap bg-background border-y border-outline-variant/30"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile text-center">
      <div data-reveal>
        <span
          class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-gold-accent mb-8"
        >format_quote</span
        >
        <blockquote class="font-headline-md text-headline-md italic mb-6">
          "Una obra maestra embotellada. AETHERIA no solo crea perfumes, captura
          momentos efímeros y los hace eternos a través del sentido más
          primitivo."
        </blockquote>
        <cite
          class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-[0.2em] uppercase not-italic text-on-surface-variant"
        >
          — VOGUE
        </cite>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
